title: Miserable Men (Howard 101 Sirius) 03-02-2008 CF56K
description:
Think your life sucks? Miserable Men is a show on Sirius Satellite Radio H101 starring men who talk about relationship hell. The Rev. Bob Levy, Al Rosenberg, Mike Morse, and Shuli, lead the charge with horror stories of dating, marriage, divorce, cheating, and the insanity that is relationships. This is a two-hour Sunday night show.

56kbps/22050 Stereo
